Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.44,0:00:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,One way or another,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.00,0:00:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,this might turn into \Nthe mother of all shit shows.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.16,0:00:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If that happens, remember that\N you "had nothing to do with it."
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.16,0:00:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Think you can do \Nthat for me, Cobra?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.62,0:00:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:04.86,0:01:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Zenba! {善波}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.96,0:01:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Every damn time, I'm stuck looking at that ass of yours!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:10.92,0:01:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're settling this today!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.14,0:01:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You on the bikes,\N stop right now!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.09,0:01:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Time's up, Linda! {輪蛇}{I'm not even making it up: https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%8D%92%E3%81%8F%E3%82%8CKNIGHT#%E8%BC%AA%E8%9B%87_%EF%BC%8DLINDA%EF%BC%8D:~:text=%5B%E7%B7%A8%E9%9B%86%5D-,%E8%BC%AA%E8%9B%87%20%EF%BC%8DLINDA%EF%BC%8D,-%5B%E7%B7%A8%E9%9B%86%5D}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.33,0:02:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You only get this lease on life \Nbecause we didn't catch you!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.36,0:02:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Zenba, let me handle \Nthe cops today.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.75,0:02:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange, just ask Hinako \Nto make me a full lunch box!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.23,0:02:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid, Hideo! \NYou're far too young for that!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.27,0:02:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Linda!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.23,0:03:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.25,0:03:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!{can't tell if this is a "shine" or a "teme-"}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.96,0:03:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the fuck are you guys?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.53,0:03:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked you who \Nthe fuck you were!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.89,0:03:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So, me and Tani beat\N 'em half to death.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.39,0:03:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Don't be stupid. \NThey barely even left a scratch.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.36,0:03:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And they even \Nused smoke bombs.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.00,0:04:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they were just some no-name team, and they only sent in the foot soldiers.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.12,0:04:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't bring a flag and they didn't have their mark on their clothes either.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.71,0:04:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone out there is making sure nobody\N finds out who's pulling the strings.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.82,0:04:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably a real careful son of a bitch. Bet he's got type-A blood and is clingy as hell.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.80,0:04:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They're taking our men \Ndown one at a time.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.31,0:04:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They knew you and I were here, \Nso they went after Keizou.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.12,0:04:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it Cobra?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.24,0:04:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You think Ibu's the type to do underhand shit like that?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.09,0:04:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, doesn't change that some trash is coming after us.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.78,0:04:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The cunning types always target your weakest link.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.06,0:04:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is off-limits for them.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.29,0:04:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I can say so far, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.21,0:04:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot. He'll be fine, \Nhe's part of Linda.{note}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.89,0:05:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, if he was a full member of Linda, that is.{idk how to shoehorn in "ichininmae"}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.98,0:05:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, some guy's at the front gate, says he's your friend.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.48,0:05:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks like a real punk.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.30,0:05:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he was here to beat the crap out of someone.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.52,0:05:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that guy. \NIt's Amano from Namigashira Tech. {missing from cc, assuming "波頭興業の天野ってんだ"}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.02,0:05:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he went to the same middle school as Haruma.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.32,0:05:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Koume, don't you \Nknow him too?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.34,0:05:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Amano...?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.63,0:05:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How's Hanazawa doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.77,0:05:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Never thought you two would end up at the same school.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.40,0:05:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Koume? \NYeah, she's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.32,0:05:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You two going out?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.71,0:05:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid. We just shout at each other because we go way back.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.62,0:05:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd just say "Hey, \Nquit messing with me!"
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.92,0:06:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't bother me.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.10,0:06:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Me and her are a thing of the past, so don't hold back.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.34,0:06:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did Amano go?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.22,0:06:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruma, I bet you know!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.74,0:06:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He ditched class! \NWhere'd he go?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.97,0:06:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How would I know?! \NWhy are you asking me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.07,0:06:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be seeing you \Nin the staff room!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.57,0:06:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You two do nothing \Nbut get in trouble!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.71,0:06:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruma, you're always getting shit for stuff Amano does, aren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.45,0:06:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up already!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.78,0:06:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.62,0:06:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruma?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.81,0:06:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruma, you've never been good with women.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.20,0:06:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.28,0:07:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about you?\NDid you see Koume already?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.64,0:07:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You and me sure got into a lot of fights back then, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.73,0:07:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I was stronger than\N you back then.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.74,0:07:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So when I heard you joined Linda, \NI couldn't believe my ears.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.00,0:07:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know, Haruma?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.21,0:07:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No signs of movement from Odawara or Seisho. {idk what's seisho, missing from cc}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.26,0:07:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing from the Demons or \Nthe Yokohama Sea Goblins either. {魔人 / 浜の海坊主 - idk anymore}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.48,0:07:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So who else has the balls \Nto take a shot at Linda?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.27,0:07:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Outside of Cobra?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.70,0:07:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ibu, I heard Chijiwa from Yokosuka \Nwas discharged from hospital last month.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.50,0:07:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The Night Bugs, then? {actually 夜行蟲 but cc has it 夜光蟲, idk why}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.30,0:08:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Haruma,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.54,0:08:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't come here as Hanazawa \NKoume's ex-boyfriend.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.82,0:08:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I just figured we could meet up and talk about the good old days.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.45,0:08:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how many guys are there in Linda, anyways?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.68,0:08:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch... It hurts.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.98,0:08:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Haruma...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.16,0:08:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The back end of the scooter...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.03,0:08:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people\N are there in Linda?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.83,0:09:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Chijiwa, Zenba put you in the hospital for a year. You been holding a grudge?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.79,0:09:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Chijiwa, isn't he #2 in Cobra?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.50,0:09:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We can deal with him right now,\N we can clean this whole mess up at once.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.97,0:09:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Amano.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.63,0:09:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.24,0:09:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.75,0:09:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Asshole!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.04,0:09:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're acting all cocky just 'cause you think you'll get credit for this.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.29,0:09:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But weren't you just chatting shit with that old friend of yours?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.02,0:09:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.46,0:09:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a limit to how many men we can throw at this, y'know? {兵隊 in cc, but we hear tamo, idk what it is, or why, and idc either}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.26,0:09:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.16,0:10:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people\N are really in Linda?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.34,0:10:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How many there {\i1}really{\i0} are.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.98,0:10:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.81,0:10:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You useless bastards! You gonna start a war with Cobra with nothing but that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.08,0:10:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Our side won't \Neven hold together.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.88,0:10:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm calling the shots because I'm the only \None here with some brains, you idiots!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.15,0:10:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Amano, if your friend is just a newbie who doesn't know shit about his team,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.89,0:10:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,why didn't you take him out there and then?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.65,0:10:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a punk like that counts as one of them!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.53,0:10:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're right...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.41,0:10:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You fuckin' idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.52,0:10:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better bring back something useful, to make up for your screwup!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.74,0:10:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you can kiss your \Npromotion goodbye!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.67,0:10:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I will make up for it...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.76,0:10:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if Linda's got more guys hiding in the dark than we think,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.24,0:11:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and even if they kill you all, the name of the Night Bugs will still echo!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.09,0:11:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're gonna crush 'em, \Nno matter what!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.29,0:11:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, so...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.37,0:11:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Amano say anything else?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.37,0:11:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.37,0:11:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure? \NNothing about me?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.12,0:11:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm sure. \NIt was all just boring small talk.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.78,0:11:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.37,0:11:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Koume, are you thinking about giving Amano another shot?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.59,0:11:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.25,0:11:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm mad!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.72,0:11:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- Fall, damn it! \N- Whoa... Don't be stupid! Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.28,0:11:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- Fall off! Fall off! \N- I can see your panties, you know?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.26,0:11:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Haruma...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.31,0:11:52.02,Thought,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait for me!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.77,0:11:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruma, am I...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.78,0:11:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the bike in front of the gate is a Ducati.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.51,0:12:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I saw it too! \NIt's been there for a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.75,0:12:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Maki?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.28,0:12:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Haruma, \Nare you free tonight?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We could meet at the parking lot at Zaimokuza...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.89,0:12:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Today? Nah, I've got \Na lot of stuff to do.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.55,0:12:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't you \Nworry about Amano.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.66,0:12:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't changed a bit.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.31,0:12:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got nothing \Nto worry about!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.42,0:12:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.70,0:12:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.75,0:12:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl didn't look too happy now, did she?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.16,0:12:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing really. Koume is pretty tough, she'll make it through.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.51,0:12:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.10,0:12:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How's Hideo?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.57,0:12:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No change.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.03,0:12:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't leave his bed and just moans all day long.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.70,0:13:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruma, if I were you, I wouldn't hang around anywhere for too long.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.05,0:13:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Maki?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.21,0:13:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, if you can't ditch school, \Ngo straight home or to Zenba's place.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.51,0:13:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?! \NPlease let me help too!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.51,0:13:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone's trying to take us on, \Nlet me fight too!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.72,0:13:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't I in Linda too?! \NHow come I get—
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.51,0:13:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, kid. I'm not hanging around you for fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.36,0:13:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you notice that \Nfly hanging around you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.17,0:13:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Around me...?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.94,0:13:40.71,Thought,,0,0,0,,You're in Linda, right? \NSo, how many of you are there, Haruma?{spoken differently to before}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.52,0:13:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'know that punk \Nyou saw yesterday?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.89,0:13:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Amano from the Night Bugs. They're the ones messing with us.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.29,0:13:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The Night Bugs?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.30,0:13:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The guys that attacked \NHideo and Phantom...?{no idea who "Phantom" is}{it's the name of the cafe place at the start}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.35,0:14:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You two were friends, \Nweren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.87,0:14:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He was my only friend from back in middle school.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.17,0:14:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Things out there aren't as easygoing as you'd think.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.48,0:14:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't tell Amano anything about Linda...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.88,0:14:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't protect Linda with a half-assed attitude!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.20,0:14:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So quit whining 'bout \Nit and sit tight.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.62,0:14:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Hideo.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.73,0:14:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking I should talk things over with Amano again.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.13,0:15:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But, if what Maki said is true, there's nothing I can do to make it up to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.61,0:15:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruma.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.04,0:15:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you in pain? \NWant me to call the nurse?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.28,0:15:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruma, it's the same for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.22,0:15:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I suck at making friends, \Njust like you do.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.13,0:15:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So I treasure each \Nand every one of 'em.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.19,0:15:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to repeat years at school and I got into fights all the time.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.40,0:15:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But thanks to that, \NI'm in the same year as you.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.23,0:15:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Maki is like Linda's manager.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.64,0:15:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So, sometimes he has to tell people the things they don't want to hear.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.35,0:15:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to understand where he's coming from.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.68,0:15:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Back when I joined,\N he chewed me out a lot too.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.88,0:15:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth is, \Nhe's worried about you.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.99,0:16:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you forget it.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.42,0:16:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I get torn to pieces, I'll still protect Linda.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.06,0:16:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Linda is all I have!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.62,0:16:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Haruma?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.69,0:16:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd you get my \Nnumber after I moved?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.41,0:16:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I give it to you?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.65,0:16:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in Linda, you know?\NI've got all sorts of connections.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.05,0:16:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.82,0:16:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I was actually planning on geting in touch anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.19,0:16:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This about the team?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.70,0:16:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'm also \Na part of one now... {チームのことだろう？俺も実際 入ってんだよ}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.66,0:16:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm already \Nknee-deep in shit.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.02,0:16:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Chijiwa, the vice leader, \Nhas already hit me over it.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.81,0:16:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Amano, we've always been\N on good terms, haven't we?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.84,0:16:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you\N saying that now?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.52,0:16:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, where \Nare you calling from?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.21,0:16:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The public phone near \Nthe East Coast Apartment Block. {東海岸団地}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.79,0:16:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right, the one \Nnear the ramen place?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.65,0:17:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'll come explain things to you in person. Just wait there.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.67,0:17:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruma, we're not very smart. {:facts:}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.51,0:17:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta break a sweat if you want to stick with your friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.33,0:17:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Even while acting all cool.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.66,0:17:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you don't break a sweat, \Nyour treasure will be taken away from you.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.14,0:17:29.27,Thought,,0,0,0,,Hideo, I don't know what the right thing is, but I'm greedy.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.00,0:17:35.28,Thought,,0,0,0,,I want to keep both my team and my old friends by any means...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.49,0:17:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let him escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.88,0:17:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Aim for his head!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.95,0:18:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Noro?\NNo! Who are you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.56,0:18:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Noro is even bigger! \NBehind him!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.71,0:18:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The three of us won't cut it!\N Run for it!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.39,0:18:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid, Haruma? Why are you wandering around in the middle of a war?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.26,0:18:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Noro, about five of them are fighting Keizou in the station parking lot. {/behind the station}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.19,0:18:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We should go to \Nthe roundabout.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.05,0:18:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.13,0:18:27.61,Thought,,0,0,0,,By the way, where \Nare you calling from?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.07,0:18:31.75,Thought,,0,0,0,,You gotta treasure your friends.{not actually a flashback...}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.68,0:18:36.84,Thought,,0,0,0,,Didn't you notice that \Nfly hanging around you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.73,0:18:43.15,Thought,,0,0,0,,Hey, Haruma, \Nare you free tonight?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.15,0:18:44.81,Thought,,0,0,0,,We could meet at the parking lot at Zaimokuza...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.35,0:18:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Koume...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.07,0:18:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you pull an all-nighter? \NMaybe you should get some sleep?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.46,0:18:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No, let's wait a little more \Nfor the information to come in.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.33,0:19:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about Haruma too.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.91,0:19:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Maki, we'll wait for tonight, \Nbut tomorrow night is when...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.00,0:19:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Linda will make a move, \Nthe way {\i1}I{\i0} want it.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.16,0:19:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,When he talks about his middle school days,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.62,0:19:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,he talks about how he treasures your friendship.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.26,0:19:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though he never knew the real reason we broke up.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.27,0:19:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to respect his feelings.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.41,0:19:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And I really don't \Nwant to trouble him.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.85,0:19:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you came all the way out here without telling Haruma?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.87,0:19:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Admit it, Hanazawa, you've still got a thing for me, don't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.10,0:19:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't give two shits about Haruma anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.69,0:19:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I only care about what Haruma's been saying about Linda.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.96,0:19:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a dead man, Noro!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.46,0:20:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Look who's talkin'!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.50,0:20:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.38,0:20:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't chicken out! There aren't many guys from Linda here!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.80,0:20:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They're tough, \Nso take 'em one at a time!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.42,0:20:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just crush those who come out, \Nand we'll win! Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.22,0:20:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanazawa, you're dating Haruma, right? Bet you two have already done it too.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.05,0:20:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, he must've told you something when you were in his arms.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.14,0:20:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the third-years complained at first... {三中}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.61,0:20:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's rough. \NIsn't Haruma by himself?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.17,0:20:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Amano...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.12,0:20:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.85,0:21:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys can go back, \NI'll take care of this.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.88,0:21:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, if you're going there to help him again today,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.14,0:21:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,because it "needs to be done" \Nor something,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.70,0:21:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,at least bring along\N a teacher or the police. {ねえ また今日も そうやって― 適当なこと言って助けに行ってあげないなら先生か おまわりさん呼んであげなよ}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.53,0:21:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay out of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.00,0:21:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If I end up crossing the wrong people, \Nwe'll both be in trouble.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.27,0:21:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you just keep quiet about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.04,0:21:22.91,Thought,,0,0,0,,Keep quiet about it...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.08,0:21:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanazawa... Hey, Hanazawa!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.39,0:21:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, Hanazawa. \NHanazawa!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.83,0:21:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We talked things over with the third-years and now we're friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.70,0:21:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of them live here.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.90,0:21:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure Haruma \Nwill come later?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.70,0:21:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.75,0:22:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure took your time.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.09,0:22:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you've started already?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.78,0:22:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They're in the closet.\N Just wait for your turn.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.87,0:22:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Amano, \Nyour girl's pretty hot.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.74,0:22:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You lied about Haruma coming, didn't you?! I'm going home!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:26.44,0:22:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you always going on about Haruma?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:28.99,0:22:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you even \Ngoing out with, Koume?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:31.86,0:22:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, just this once, \Nlet me go all the way.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:34.72,0:22:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! \NWho even are those people?!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:37.42,0:22:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no! Never!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:39.73,0:22:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:42.27,0:22:43.59,Thought,,0,0,0,,Hanazawa...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:49.03,0:22:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanazawa!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:53.04,0:22:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, since we couldn’t do it back then, we can do it now, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:58.81,0:23:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? How does that sound?\NMight make it easier to talk things over.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:03.87,0:23:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you kidding?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:05.40,0:23:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what your deal is, \Nbut I came here to tell you one thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:09.68,0:23:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit dragging both of us into this stupid little game of yours!{avoiding the "yoku"}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:16.98,0:23:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You bitch!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:19.45,0:23:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking for it!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.86,0:23:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Night Bugs... Night Bugs...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.47,0:23:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Night Bugs... \NAre you one of the Night Bugs?!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:36.71,0:23:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like you're real curious about Haruma, eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:43.57,0:23:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, cut it out!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:45.35,0:23:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that? \NInformation about Linda?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:47.99,0:23:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, were you the one that crashed into me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:10.94,0:24:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:13.59,0:24:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Help me, somebody!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:36.94,0:24:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Koume? Ah... Hideo!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:41.61,0:24:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hideo!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:42.85,0:24:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go, you dumbass!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:44.40,0:24:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't have the guts, \NI'll kill him myself!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:49.84,0:24:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go, Haruma!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:52.30,0:24:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Amano, what the hell \Nare you doing here?!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:05.19,0:25:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Koume!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:19.08,0:25:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy is Fujiki!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:20.53,0:25:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Fujiki Keizou!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:21.82,0:25:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:29.23,0:25:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, guys... Fujiki is...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:51.78,0:25:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't been to \Nthis café in months.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:54.55,0:25:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I was on my way back from visiting a friend's house.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:57.58,0:25:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:59.29,0:26:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajime started crying, so I went for a walk to show him the sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:04.97,0:26:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks pretty messed up around here, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:08.39,0:26:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no point in asking Tani what happened, is there?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:16.38,0:26:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Zenba, the Night Bugs didn't have \Na backup plan. Let's crush them now!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:21.27,0:26:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, Hideo escaped \Nfrom the hospital.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:24.77,0:26:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:46.61,0:26:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, that's noisy! \NWho's that show-off?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:50.14,0:26:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like they've removed the silencer from the muffler.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:53.17,0:26:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Zenba's bike!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:55.61,0:26:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like something big is about to go down.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:58.51,0:27:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one of Linda's \Nsignals, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:11.36,0:27:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gone! Both Fujiki and Noro are gone!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:18.73,0:27:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed about two weeks of school after that.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:25.01,0:27:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He transferred schools \Nduring that time.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:28.67,0:27:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He got in trouble with some of \Nthe third-year boys, and got caught.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:36.59,0:27:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruma never asked about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:39.62,0:27:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He just kept quiet and never asked \Nwhat happened to Amano...
Dialogue: 10,0:27:48.61,0:27:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he knew \Nsomething was wrong.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:52.17,0:27:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes to stuff like that,\N he's so thoughtful, it's almost annoying.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:19.52,0:28:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All of Linda has disappeared.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:21.10,0:28:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We've looked all over the city,
Dialogue: 10,0:28:23.38,0:28:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's no sign of Noro, Fujiki, Maki, or even their chief, Zenba.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:28.74,0:28:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe our first hit \Nscared them shitless?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:32.22,0:28:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They ran for it? \NSo we won on guts alone!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:35.39,0:28:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All of Linda has disappeared?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:38.08,0:28:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I want everyone who can move here, right fuckin' now.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:42.33,0:28:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ll sweep the streets and wipe them out one by one!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:47.62,0:28:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ibu.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:49.33,0:28:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All of Linda that went into hiding are on the move.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:57.25,0:29:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ibu, they've just passed through \Nthe residential area of ​​Kamakurayama.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:05.77,0:29:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ibu, the rest of the Night Bugs \Nare at the seaside park.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:17.05,0:29:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ibu, you don't think Linda was waiting for that?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:25.79,0:29:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Two members of Linda passed \Nthrough the backstreets of the 134.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:35.62,0:29:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A few more of them have just passed the Tsujido intersection.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:40.68,0:29:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, there's more coming through. Four, five, six...
Dialogue: 10,0:29:43.66,0:29:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Six just passed by, \NI'll follow them.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:51.44,0:29:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ibu, they're all \Nheading for the coast.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:54.95,0:29:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There's another one!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:58.76,0:30:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Chijiwa! Chijiwa!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:00.37,0:30:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:01.36,0:30:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on the police radio, and I picked up some weird chatter.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:06.20,0:30:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's more of them! Two more are coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:08.80,0:30:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's those Cobra guys!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:11.37,0:30:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They keep coming! Three more! \NAnd now another two!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:16.01,0:30:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Linda?\NDid he say Linda?!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:17.98,0:30:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They're passing through the seaside park now.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:20.25,0:30:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,T-There's more of them!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:21.74,0:30:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiots! It's right around the corner! \NSomeone go see what's going on!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:24.77,0:30:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:28.25,0:30:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you find them, \Nkill 'em on the spot!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:31.77,0:30:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here too… three more of them! \NTheir numbers are insane!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:36.44,0:30:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Somebody call the boss!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:43.58,0:30:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't look like \Nanyone passed by.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:45.67,0:30:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even hear any bikes.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:52.27,0:30:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So they abandoned you guys?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:56.02,0:31:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When the war kicked off, you acted like you'd swallow Linda whole,
Dialogue: 10,0:31:00.34,0:31:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,so I even considered \Nbacking you guys.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:04.16,0:31:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess it never \Nwas gonna work out.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:05.96,0:31:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Noro, Fujiki, Maki, \Nand even that newbie kid...
Dialogue: 10,0:31:09.13,0:31:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't take \Ndown a single one.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:10.85,0:31:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are like a lizard's tail, \None I'm cutting off and throwing away.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:15.60,0:31:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What’s that supposed to mean?! \NWhat are you saying?!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:28.21,0:31:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The boss isn't picking up.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:29.53,0:31:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't pick up? \NWhat about his cell?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:32.18,0:31:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Same for that too!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:32.95,0:31:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We need him to send men now! \NLike right fucking now!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:37.33,0:31:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Cobra?!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:39.04,0:31:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything unusual \Nfrom them?!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:43.24,0:31:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing. \NThey're keeping quiet.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:47.07,0:31:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Damn it...
Dialogue: 10,0:31:49.65,0:31:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! What the hell are those Linda bastards doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:53.45,0:31:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't they \Nsupposed to be gone?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:55.27,0:31:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, didn't they just run away?! \NWhat the hell...
Dialogue: 10,0:31:58.86,0:32:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The boss... Did you get through to the boss? Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:04.38,0:32:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, then you all \Ncharge in and die!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:07.36,0:32:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Chijiwa!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:11.12,0:32:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading back. \NI'll go talk things over.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:07.88,0:33:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Zenba, you bastard!\NYou set me up!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:12.05,0:33:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the hell did you come from?! \NWhat are you, really?!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:17.05,0:33:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What the fuck is going on?!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:24.07,0:33:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Move it!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:27.65,0:33:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Chijiwa!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:42.96,0:33:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Chijiwa!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:54.36,0:33:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait! \NSomeone give me a ride!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:26.16,0:34:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You know you're weaker than me, \Nbut you still wanna take me on?!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:30.11,0:34:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You little punk!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:22.61,0:35:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't kill me... {/hold back}
Dialogue: 10,0:35:23.84,0:35:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't kill me, please...
Dialogue: 10,0:35:28.35,0:35:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't kill me, Haruma...
Dialogue: 10,0:35:32.96,0:35:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruma...
Dialogue: 10,0:35:35.93,0:35:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... forgive me.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:42.20,0:35:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me... somebody...
Dialogue: 10,0:35:48.02,0:35:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please... help...
Dialogue: 10,0:36:20.17,0:36:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit...
Dialogue: 10,0:36:51.34,0:36:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Zenba really is amazing, isn't he?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:55.91,0:36:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, he ended up marrying someone like you, Hinako.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:00.15,0:37:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you all about the loose cannon some other time.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:03.03,0:37:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Loose cannon?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:04.72,0:37:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Once he leaves the house, \Nyou never know when he'll come back.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:12.71,0:37:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you jump \Nout at me like that?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:14.44,0:37:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Koume, the thing \Nabout boys is...
Dialogue: 10,0:37:16.98,0:37:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always better to\N be kind with them.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:20.39,0:37:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, you idiot? Looks like you've still got some fight in you.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:23.57,0:37:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruma, what \Nhappened to your face?!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:28.33,0:37:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shut up. \NI'm not telling you shit.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:32.12,0:37:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Not telling!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:34.15,0:37:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it slow, okay? \NOne step at a time.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:40.04,0:37:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we just stay \Nlike this for a while?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:41.91,0:37:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's with you?! \NLet go, you idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:44.78,0:37:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- Way to go, Koume!\N- Way to go, Koume!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:47.98,0:37:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re not lonely\N anymore, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:49.71,0:36:57.01,Song,,0,0,0,,A white cloud sprawls across a wide, open sky.{突き抜けるような空に白い雲が寝そべる}
Dialogue: 10,0:36:57.01,0:37:04.25,Song,,0,0,0,,{影のシャワーをあげて　笑いかけるひまわり}Sunflowers shower me in soft shade as they smile my way.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:04.72,0:37:12.73,Song,,0,0,0,,I cried so much that I couldn't see anything at all.{泣いてばかりで　見えなかった}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:12.73,0:37:20.07,Song,,0,0,0,,But now the whole world is \Nbeginning to open up! Whoa, whoa!{世界ごとは開きはじめている　ウォウ　ウォウ}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:20.74,0:37:28.33,Song,,0,0,0,,With the gentleness only you possess,{あなただけが持っている優しさで　ほら}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:28.33,0:37:35.20,Song,,0,0,0,,the traces of my tears begin to shine like emeralds!{涙の跡　光り出すエメラルド}{at least, assuming I hear the start right}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:35.20,0:37:42.84,Song,,0,0,0,,Even the sadness I'd tucked\N away turns into courage.{しまいこんだ悲しみも　勇気に変えて}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:42.84,0:37:50.02,Song,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure these feeling reach your heart.{この想い　いつでも胸に届けるからね}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:50.06,0:38:00.39,Song,,0,0,0,,Gently... softly... I want you to feel my love.{そっと　そっと　恋を感じてほしい}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:52.10,0:37:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You made so many friends, Haruma. \NYou're not lonely anymore, are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:17.46,0:38:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're through to the Zenba household.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:19.32,0:38:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We're terribly sorry, \Nbut we're away right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:22.46,0:38:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have a message for us, \Nplease leave it after the tone.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:29.34,0:38:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Zenba? \NIt's Adachi of the Night Bugs.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:35.68,0:38:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Some guy I kept at my side, and a few hot-headed punks, acted on their own.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:43.62,0:38:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and about that punk kid Amano or whatever he was called.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:49.46,0:38:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it doesn't look like he'll ever be able to ride again. I made sure of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:55.81,0:39:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We only took out one of your guys,\N but we've got eight in the hospital.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:01.90,0:39:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,From where you're standing, \Nthat should make things about even.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:08.47,0:39:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But the thing is...
Dialogue: 10,0:39:10.97,0:39:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We may have backed \Ndown this time,
Dialogue: 10,0:39:14.35,0:39:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but don't go thinking you can walk all over us!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:17.35,0:39:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you want war, \NI'm ready anytime.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:21.62,0:39:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, whatever.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:26.03,0:39:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just say one more thing...
Dialogue: 10,0:39:30.43,0:39:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There are still any number of \Nguys aiming for your heads.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:36.80,0:39:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that, \NZenba Naito. {七五十  (750 - the cc of his bike), the first character of each kun-yomi reading together is "na-i-to"}
Dialogue: 10,0:39:41.42,0:39:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,See you around.
